body:
I ain't sure if "automagically" was a typo:
[tensorflow/tools/graph_transforms/transform_utils.h#L269](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/tools/graph_transforms/transform_utils.h#L269) talks about an "automagical" registration
so, why wouldn't the README mean it that way?
